 src/http/v2/ngx_http_v2.c         | 85 ++++++++++++++++++++++---------
 src/http/v3/ngx_http_v3_request.c | 60 +++++++++++++++++-----
 3 files changed, 117 insertions(+), 40 deletions(-)

